The molecular dynamics simulations provide a comprehensive analysis of electrolyte-graphene interactions, emphasizing key parameters influencing droplet behavior, wettability, and electrostatic interactions. Key findings include the equilibrium conformation of the electrolyte droplet on a 40 nm \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
